# Frontend build-time config for Vite. Copy to `.env.local` for local overrides.
# (Vite only exposes vars prefixed with VITE_ to the client, and inlines them at build.)

# Backend ORIGIN — scheme + host, no trailing path or slash.
# Leave UNSET to use the relative "/api/v1" (dev proxy / Vercel /api rewrite, same-origin, no CORS).
# Set it to call the backend directly (cross-origin — the Go server must then send CORS headers):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://all-life-548264816971.asia-southeast1.run.app
